import os               Import the os module.

help(os)                From within the interactive environment, this prints a list of os
                        functions and other features.

os.listdir()            List directory. Returns a list, each element of which is a string
                        containing a file name.

os.chdir(string)        Change directory. The string can contain either a relative or a
                        full path name.

os.getcwd()             Get Current Working Directory. Returns the full path name of
                        the current directory, in a string.